InCR Instantiate a new Product Training Procedure
UpCR Update details relating to Product Training Procedure
CoCR Control the processing of Product Training Procedure
EcCR Accept, verify, etc. aspects of Product Training Procedure processing
ExCR Execute an available automated action for Product Training Procedure
RqCR Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Product Training Procedure
ReCR Retrieve details about any aspect of Product Training Procedure
